# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# data — keep synthesized JSON (needed at build time), ignore raw/CSV/progress/logs
**/data/outscraper-plumbers.csv
**/data/raw/.scrape-progress.json
**/data/synthesized/.synthesis-progress.json
**/data/logs/

# dependencies
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
**/coverage

# next.js
/.next/
**/out/

# production
**/build

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files and secrets
.env*
service-account.json

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# monorepo
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.env*
.turbo
